com.io7m.jspatial.quadtrees

Interface QuadTreeSDType<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The precise type of quadtree members.
    All Superinterfaces:
    QuadTreeType<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    QuadTreeSDBasic, QuadTreeSDLimit, QuadTreeSDPrune, QuadTreeSDPruneLimit

    public interface QuadTreeSDType<T extends QuadTreeMemberType<T>>
extends QuadTreeType<T>
    The interface provided by quadtree implementations that distinguish between static (immovable) and dynamic (movable) objects.

    • Method Detail

      • quadTreeInsertSD

        boolean quadTreeInsertSD(T item,
                         SDType type)
        Insert the object item into the quadtree. The object will be given the categorization type.

        The function returns false if the object could not be inserted for any reason (perhaps due to being too large).

        Parameters:
        item - The object to insert
        type - The categorization of the object
        Returns:
        true if the object was inserted

      • quadTreeSDClearDynamic

        void quadTreeSDClearDynamic()
        Remove all dynamic (movable) objects from the tree.
